<template>
  <vBasePage
    :searchOptions="searchOptions"
    :tableOption="tableOption"
    @rowBlock="rowClick"
  ></vBasePage>
</template>

<script>
import vBasePage from "../../BasePage/BasePage";
import FileManagerApi from "../webapi/FileManager";
import moment from "moment";
import config from "@/config/index";

var TableUniqueId = "FileId";
var FileSource = {
  "1": "生产文件",
  "2": "物流文件"
};
var Platform = {
  "1": "DTS",
  "2": "OEM"
};
export default {
  data() {
    var _ = this;
    return {
      searchOptions: {
        searchOptions: {
          requiredCondition: false
        },
        exportUrl: FileManagerApi.GetPushExceptionFileList,
        seleFunc: {
          export: true,
          search: true
        },
        search_controls: [
          {
            type: "v_text",
            title: "上传点编号",
            key: "PlaceId"
          },
          {
            type: "v_text",
            title: "枪号",
            key: "EquipmentNumber"
          },
          {
            type: "v_singleSelect",
            title: "文件类型",
            key: "FileSource",
            data: [
              {
                id: '1',
                value: '生产文件',
              },
              {
                id: '2',
                value: '物流文件',
              }
            ],
            selectkey: "id",
            selectvalue: "value"
          },
          {
            type: "v_singleSelect",
            title: "文件来源",
            key: "Platform",
            data: [
              {
                id: '1',
                value: 'DTS',
              },
              {
                id: '2',
                value: 'OEM',
              }
            ],
            selectkey: "id",
            selectvalue: "value"
          },
          {
            type: "v_text",
            title: "文件名",
            key: "FileName"
          },
          {
            type: "v_datetime",
            title: "上传开始日期",
            key: "UpdateTimeStartDate"
            //defdate: moment(new Date()).add(-1, 'months').format("YYYY-MM-DD")
          },
          {
            type: "v_datetime",
            title: "上传结束日期",
            key: "UpdateTimeEndDate"
          }
        ]
      },
      tableOption: {
        tableId: "pullabnormal",
        tableName: "推送异常文件列表",
        url: config.pgyerApiUrl + FileManagerApi.GetPushExceptionFileList.options.url,
        method: FileManagerApi.GetPushExceptionFileList.options.method,
        uniqueId: TableUniqueId,
        columns: [
          {
            field: "fileName",
            title: "文件名",
            align: "center"
          },
          {
            field: "placeId",
            title: "上传点编号",
            align: "center"
          },
          {
            field: "equipmentNumber",
            title: "枪号",
            align: "center",
          },
          {
            field: "fileSource",
            title: "文件类型（生产、物流）",
            align: "center",
            formatter: function(val, row) {
              return FileSource[row.fileSource];
            }
          },
          {
            field: "platform",
            title: "文件来源（OEM、DTS）",
            align: "center",
            formatter: function(val, row) {
              return Platform[row.platform];
            }
          },
          {
            field: "updateTime",
            title: "上传日期",
            align: "center",
            formatter: function(val, row) {
              return moment(val).format("YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm");
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    };
  },
  methods: {
    rowClick: function(rowItem, element, baseObject) {
      console.log(element);
      debugger;
    }
  },
  components: { vBasePage }
};
</script>
